\pard\f0\fs28  {\b  C. leucomelaena} Hayek, {\i Prodr. Fl. Penins. Balcan.}{\b  2}: 758 (1931), described from Albania, is like {\b 74} but has arachnoid-hairy leaves, triangular-ovate, non-spiny appendages, and pappus 1/3-1/2 as long as the achene. Its status requires confirmation.
\par

